      <title>印度将斥资约35亿美元购买更多侦察机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/india-to-spend-about-3-5-billion-for-more-surveillance-planes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度将从航空巨头空中客车公司购买十几架海上侦察机，成本估计为 2900 亿卢比（35 亿美元），试图增强其在日益动荡的印度洋地区的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/india-to-spend-about-3-5-billion-for-more-surveillance-planes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 15:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
